room_title: Escape room "The Locker Room - Bisby's Briefcase" by Escape House in Rexburg
room_description: Professor Bisby just can’t catch a break. The baseball team has pestered him from day one. Usually, it is all in good fun, but this time they have gone too far. They stole and hid his briefcase which has the wedding ring for the girl of his dreams. Help Bisby, he’s planned a special proposal for tonight. He will never find another girl. This is do or die. Can you save Bisby's proposal before it is too late?
